text.section:
In addition to the duties set forth elsewhere in this subtitle, the State Advisory Council shall:
Maintain liaison with:
The State Department of Education;
County boards of education;
Private and parochial schools;
County commissions; and
Physical fitness agencies in other states and in the federal government;
Consult with and advise county advisory councils on their physical fitness programs;
Give out information on physical fitness programs in this State by publication, advertisement, conferences, workshops, programs, lectures, and other means;
Collect and assemble pertinent information that is available from other agencies of this State; and
Generally promote physical fitness in this State.
